The molecular formula of 2-(3-amino-2-methylpropyl)oxazinan-3-one is C10H19N1O2. 

Thus, the total number of atoms in the molecule is:
Carbon (C): 10 atoms
Hydrogen (H): 19 atoms
Nitrogen (N): 1 atom
Oxygen (O): 2 atoms

Therefore, the total number of atoms in 2-(3-amino-2-methylpropyl)oxazinan-3-one is 32.
